DESCRIPTION_COPY: Kopisha konke okungeni isikhwama esibhetshe kuclipboard.
DESCRIPTION_IMPORT: Bechanjela zonke izinto kubhiniti yokususa ngendlela .json.
DESCRIPTION_SETTINGS_ENABLED: Isilungiselelo esigcwele sokuvula noma kuvimba konke ukusebenza kweTrashbin+
DESCRIPTION_SETTINGS_SHOW_WIDGET: Bonisa ikhona yekhanda ngaphandle kwebar yesondlo ekugcineni umlando okudlalwayo ngoku ngokushesha
DESCRIPTION_SETTINGS_AUTOPLAY: Qala ukudlala imiziki ngokuzenzekelayo uma i-Spotify ivulwe noma isiphindezelo sifaka
DESCRIPTION_SETTINGS_QUEUE_TRASHBIN: Faka izithombe zedolobha ezinguqulunga ngasinye kumuziki wakho ukuze kube lula ukuphatha
DESCRIPTION_SETTINGS_TRACKLIST_TRASHBIN: Faka izithombe zedolobha ezadlulwa kumabhasi kumalini nezinhlobo zomculo ukuze kuthuluzekwe ngokushesha
DESCRIPTION_SETTINGS_PLAYLIST_MONITOR: Phinda uzive ngokuzenzakalelayo kusindzimanzindzimana seSpotify ngokubuyisa phansi uduli lwakho lwesikhathi esheshayo
DESCRIPTION_SETTINGS_TRASH_ON_NEXT_HOTKE: Cima ngokuzenzakalelayo umbhali wamanje uma usebenzisa i-Ctrl+Right keyboard shortcut ukuze uphumelela kumbhali olandelayo
